{"tid":2161139,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"留任與杯葛立法會後的行動藍圖","createTime":"2020-08-17T11:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T15:50:46.000Z","uid":324193,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a8946af19190d95f8bd6cc5705d890caf2e0c5d5","tid":2161139,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:39:24.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">關鍵並非留任與杯葛的決定本身，而是留任與杯葛之後的行動藍圖，政客有責任說明他們下的決定會如何幫助抗爭運動走下去</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">如果現任議員留任，他們有幾樣事情必須做：</span><br />\n<br />\n1 公開承諾只會擔任一年的額外任期。<br />\n2 公開承諾不會贊成任何議案，即是只投「反對」或「棄權」。<br />\n3 就每一政府議案提出反建議。 <br />\n4 留任議員擔任本土派的代理人。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">如果現屆議員不留任，抗爭陣營共同建立民間的連結網絡：</span><br />\n<br />\n1 利用區議會網絡建立民意諮詢網絡。<br />\n2 初選參與者成立「政策研究會議」。<br />\n<br />\n全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%95%99%E4%BB%BB%E8%88%87%E6%9D%AF%E8%91%9B%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E8%97%8D%E5%9C%96/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2595%2599%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%259D%25AF%25E8%2591%259B%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%2597%258D%25E5%259C%2596%2F&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21NTdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=ffb5467a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2595%2599%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%259D%25AF%25E8%2591%259B%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%2597%258D%25E5%259C%2596%2F&h=fef80e4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%95%99%E4%BB%BB%E8%88%87%E6%9D%AF%E8%91%9B%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E8%97%8D%E5%9C%96/</a><br />\n<br />\n作者<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NoCagedMan/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNoCagedMan%2F&d=hvnZYtOEd